  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You draw upon your channel energy to enhance the protective ability of your shield and those of allies while they are adjacent to you.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Channel energy, 3d6 proficiency with a shield.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a swift action, you can spend a use of your channel energy to grant yourself a +2 deflection bonus while using a shield. This bonus lasts 1 minute per cleric level or effective cleric level. While you benefit from this bonus, allies with shields also gain a +2 deflection bonus while they are adjacent to you.",
